  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nHelm create should add options to create security policies, as it is a known best practice to enable security policies, notably, to run as non root, to have a read only file system , drop linux capabilities and so on.\r\nBy adding the option to create security policies we are making it easier to do the right thing.\r\n\r\ncc @bacongobbler @unguiculus @scottrigby @rimusz \r\n",
